data.name: lblResetAllData.Text
data.value:
The game metadata is cached locally on your computer and only updated when it changes to conserve bandwidth.
This will flush the cache, clear the in-memory data, then re-download and parse everything from scratch.

data.name: lblCheckEvents.Text
data.value:
Battleground Europe Game Monitor polls the Wiretap server for new game events dynamically between every 1 - 15 minutes, depending on the type of event.
Use this to force an immediate manual check for any new events.

data.name: lblSleepMode.Text
data.value:
When in sleep mode, Battleground Europe Game Monitor will "hibernate", using as little memory/cpu as possible and no network bandwidth.
Waking up again will require an approx {0}kb download of data to re-establish game state.
